style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: AdobeHeitiStd-Regular; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">保荐机构及发行人律师应当对发行人是否存在上述事项进行核查，并对是否构成重大违法行为及再融资的法律障碍发表意见。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
